data.name: Instructions
data.value:
1.该工具用于光方立软件制作，需使用配套的硬件 才能使用。
2.动画运行的方式按动画组中从上往下依次执行， 当所有动画组运行结束后，会自动从头开始。
3.动画操作中，所有坐标系的起点均为朝向自已的 左下角为原点，即X，Y，Z均为0(视角发生改变时， 该值表示的位置会不同)。
4.动画组与索引表的复制操作，请勿在多个软件中执 行，这样会因为资源不相同而导致出错。
注：1）画图时，按住键盘CTRL键再点击画板，是用 来清除已画的点。 2）动画组列表选项位置可以直接鼠标托动。 3) 电脑仿真的速度与实际有所区别，请以实际 光立方为主。

data.name: Instructions_en
data.value:
1. This tool is designed for light cube software and requires the corresponding hardware.
2. Animations are executed sequentially from the top of the animation group to the bottom. When all animation groups have finished running, they automatically restart from the beginning.
3. During animation operations, all coordinate systems begin with the bottom-left corner facing the user's own coordinate system, with the X, Y, and Z coordinates all at 0 (the positions represented by these values ​​will change if the viewing angle changes).
4. Do not copy animation groups and index tables across multiple instances of this program, as this may cause errors due to different resource ids.
Note: 1) while drawing, hold down the Ctrl key on your keyboard and click the drawing board to clear previously drawn points. 2) you can move the options in the animation group list directly with your mouse. 3) computer rendering speed may differ from actual speed; please refer to the actual light cube.
